{"word":"ἐξουσιάζω","slug":"ἐξουσιάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐξουσιάζω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prec.\">prec.</a>] <b>exercise authority <a href='B:490 22:25'>Lk 22:25</a>; <a href='B:530 7:4'>1 Cor 7:4</a>.—</b>In wordplay <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔξεστι\">ἔξεστι</a></el>: <el>πάντα μοι ἔξεστιν ἀλλ</el>’ <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκ\">οὐκ</a> ἐγὼ ἐξουσιασϑήσομαι <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπό\">ὑπό</a> τινος</el> every thing is under my authority, but I refuse to be ‘authorized’ by any thing, i.e. be under the control of any thing <b><a href='B:530 6:12'>6:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐξουσία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐξοχή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}